        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 1 at 6:04PM CDT until May 1 at 6:30PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 603 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 4 miles east of
Texline, or 14 miles southeast of Clayton, moving southeast at 20
mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Texline.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
